rows.label: qst702702_msg0001
rows.name:
So, those are the monsters blocking
traffic across the bridge, then?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't want trouble, but that bridge
is simply not your place!

rows.label: qst702702_msg0101
rows.name:
I see now.
They're doing a grand job of blocking
the way, aren't they?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0102
rows.name:
Some people just don't know when to
cut their losses and quit, I guess.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0103
rows.name:
That's funny, coming from you.
I'm starting to feel for the monsters.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0104
rows.name: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?!

rows.label: qst702702_msg0105
rows.name:
He's saying he looks forward to
working with you. In his own way.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0106
rows.name:
Now then...
Is everyone ready?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0201
rows.name:
I see now.
They're doing a grand job of blocking
the way, aren't they?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0202
rows.name:
Some people just don't know when to
cut their losses and quit, I guess.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0203
rows.name:
That's funny, coming from you.
I'm starting to feel for the monsters.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0204
rows.name: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?!

rows.label: qst702702_msg0205
rows.name: ...Laura-sama, should we intervene..?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0206
rows.name: Nah...

rows.label: qst702702_msg0207
rows.name:
They're just each saying what they're
thinking, and that's no easy thing.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0208
rows.name:
Sure, they might butt heads
sometimes, but that doesn't mean
they'll kill each other, right?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0209
rows.name: Who the hell do you think you are?!

rows.label: qst702702_msg0210
rows.name:
Good line. Why don't you look in
a mirror and ask yourself that?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0211
rows.name: Urgh, I hate this guy's guts...

rows.label: qst702702_msg0212
rows.name:
Ah, friendly banter between comrades
is music to my ears. I'm sure that
together, we can go far!

rows.label: qst702702_msg0213
rows.name: ...Looks like they want to join the party.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0214
rows.name:
In that case, why don't we give them
a warm welcome?
